description.narrative: UNICEF supported implementation of county specific Social Behavior Change Communication and complementary feeding strategies and reached 13 targeted counties. Baby friendly community initiative ( BFCI) reached 770 mother support groups and 149,520 mothers with new-born. Early initiation of breastfeeding reached 78%. Iron folate supplementation covered 76% of pregnant mothers. | Status:Partially Met | As-of Date:30/06/2018
